Get ready for a tail-wagging good time in these rescue adventures with the
PAW Patrol! Get ready to save the day in Adventure Bay with Ryder and his
team of heroic puppies: Marshall the firedog, Skye the daredevil flying pup,
Chase the police dog, Rubble the construction pup, Rocky the recycling pup,
and Zuma the water rescue dog. The pups have some watery rescues to tend to
when they help sea turtle hatchlings cross a road and lead a beached baby
whale back to its mother. Next, the pups help their animal friends when
they rescue a lost kitty from the bay, help a baby gosling fly home with
his flock, and track down a baby elephant that escaped from a circus train!
Then, PAW Patrol is on a roll as they come to the rescue of Mayor Goodway
when she gets stuck in a hot air balloon and when her pet chicken, Chickaletta,
gets lost! From fighting fires to fixing train tracks to defeating snow monsters,
for PAW Patrol, no job is too big, no pup is too small!

Produced by Spin Master Entertainment, TVOKids and Nickelodeon Productions.


Cap'n Turbot accidentally stumbles into a secret cavern.
When the PAW Patrol rescues him, they find an incomplete
treasure map. The adventure is on as the pups follow clues.
